channel.title: Status page help, nobody answers on the real page
channel.description:
I'm losing VPS time because my server won't go up, it's online and I'm 100% sure of that, I've had people log in from a different advertisement.
I've been waiting for at least 10 hours now, my server still hasn't went up. It says be patient when I try to register it again. http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php?server=65.75.245.21 I did go on the link given on my VPS' browser, and it said activated/approved or whatever.
